rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0004
rows.name:
I bet a lot of these
people are pilgrims.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Yes, that's correct.
Large numbers of people
come here every day.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0006
rows.name:
And what you can see ahead
is the cathedral.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0008
rows.name:
What'd ya think?
Ya can feel the Holy See's authority,
can't ya?

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0009
rows.name: What are YOU so proud of, Turtle-chan?

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0011
rows.name:
We have prepared rooms for you all.
They are on the left as you
enter the cathedral.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0012
rows.name: We actually get to stay in cathedral?!

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0013
rows.name: You are our honored guests, after all.
